          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill revises provisions that govern the appointment of administrative law judges. </p> <p>Specifically, it provides that administrative law judges: (1) serve in positions in the competitive service, and (2) must be appointed by the head of a federal agency.</p>]]></text>
